13. Write a program to find the sum of the given series 1+2+3+ . . . . . . (n terms) 

Input: n = 1
Output: 1
Explanation: For n = 1, the sum will be 1.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
use formula :n*(n+1)/2
-----------------------------

class Solution {
  public:
  
    long long seriesSum(long n) 
    {
        n=n*(n+1)/2;
        
    }
};

